{"tid":461672,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼力捧《銀河守護隊2》《雷神3》爭電影奬","createTime":"2017-11-08T00:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T00:29:33.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"badaccaace429cfc41da13c8036ed28021848a39","tid":461672,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:35:27.000Z","msg":"雖然離明年 3 月的壓軸奧斯卡獎還有幾個月時間，但迪士尼似乎已經等不及要把自家今年的作品展示給會員們看，希望有會員青睞他們今年的電影作品，成功入圍甚至得獎讓電影鍍金。就在日前迪士尼發佈了一個迪士尼工會獎的網頁，提供美國電影學會會員參考他們今年的強力作品時，我們發現裡面有兩部漫威的電影也在榜單上，分別是剛剛上映的《雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏》（Thor: Ragnarok），以及票房嚇嚇叫的《星際異攻隊2》（Guardians of Galaxy Vol.2）。<br />\n<br />\n在迪士尼的「供你參考」網頁中，列出了包括《美女與野獸》（Beauty and the Beast）、《可可夜總會》（Coco）、《Cars 3：閃電再起》（Cars 3），以及短片動畫《Lou》，而最下面則是兩部漫威的續集作品。雖然說迪士尼的動畫作品一直都是奧斯卡的常勝軍，不過這次如此大力地推薦兩部超級英雄電影著實有趣，因為除了技術面的獎項以外，從迪士尼做的圖卡看起來，他們更希望把在《星際異攻隊2》裡面，他們特地混音製作的舞曲〈Guardians Inferno〉推向最佳原創歌曲獎。（沒錯就是大衛赫索霍夫（David Hasselhoff）獻聲口白的那首）<br />\n<br />\n這兩部漫威超級英雄電影的確都是相當有導演個人風格的作品，《雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏》裡面我們可以感受到《吸血鬼的家庭詩篇》（What We Do In the Shadow）導演塔伊加維迪提（Taika Waititi）驚人且獨特的幽默感，而《星際異攻隊2》導演詹姆斯岡恩（James Gunn）除了延續前作的歡樂風格以外，在這次的配樂上也精挑細選了非常多經典的 80 年代歌曲，也難怪迪士尼會如此提前開始推廣自家的這兩部作品，或許也真的會成為今年獎季的黑馬也說不定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.waltdisneystudiosawards.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waltdisneystudiosawards.com&d=AOP3rO6paCFAFoPnom7SaE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d973d3f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.waltdisneystudiosawards.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/media2.slashfilm.com/slashfilm/wp/wp-content/images/thorragnarok-awardsconsideration.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmedia2.slashfilm.com%2Fslashfilm%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fimages%2Fthorragnarok-awardsconsideration.jpg&h=f7c6880b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/media2.slashfilm.com/slashfilm/wp/wp-content/images/guardians2-awardsconsideration.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmedia2.slashfilm.com%2Fslashfilm%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fimages%2Fguardians2-awardsconsideration.jpg&h=d1804f5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47094e0d2d703ca13af1930cc357b87ed5de321e","tid":461672,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/03133/transformers_3133892e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F03133%2Ftransformers_3133892e.jpg&h=391a950e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f4a6ac4663d265553621480ede1d08902fd068","tid":461672,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:52:52.000Z","msg":"志在參與"},{"pid":"8bebac5cc4d3f32d4e737fb2d141f324a0307216","tid":461672,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/03133/transformers_3133892e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F03133%2Ftransformers_3133892e.jpg&h=391a950e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a115cc659c6d7156f30bc7d58f4d3430d48eade","tid":461672,"uid":154684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"幾大都谷下佢啦<br />\n人地suicide squad上年都執左個技術獎"},{"pid":"d495fa70e7f9e646a370523460c9fd2048926789","tid":461672,"uid":149201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾大都谷下佢啦<br />\n人地suicide squad上年都執左個技術獎</blockquote><br />\n啱呀，求其推幾套電影<br />\n求其執返幾個獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c965cec9149ba59da6efd88b9e79750cecbf65a","tid":461672,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/0313